<br>
Do this following command:<br>
<br>
/ho MA /assist &lt;name of main assist&gt;<br>
<br>
What will happen is a new button will appear at the end of your mouse pointer (in game of course) and you can put it in whatever your assist key spot is, then what ever key you replace, click on the screen as if you are going to drop it.<br>
<br>
If you get in the habit of doing this, there should be no reason for people being on the wrong mob.<br>
<br>
Thought I'd pass this along...<br>
<br>
Ronoh Wrathmore<br>
Ecce Neco (leader)<br>
59 Iksar Shadow Knight<br>
Weilder of Greenmist<br>
