<br>
Syntax is:<br>
<br>
/hotbutton &lt;button color, 1 2 3, etc&gt; &lt;command, /assist, /targ, etc&gt;<br>
<br>
example: /hotbutton 4 /assist Khuul<br>
<br>
Hope it helps. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=123190">

